    "title": "SAVE (Survival after Veno-Arterial ECMO) Score",
    "desc": "The Survival after Veno-Arterial ECMO (SAVE) Score predicts survival in adult patients after ECMO for refractory cardiogenic shock.",
    "data": {
        "orgreference": [
