                "text": "Schmidt M, Burrell A, Roberts L, et al. Predicting survival after ECMO for refractory cardiogenic shock: the survival after veno-arterial-ECMO (SAVE)-score. Eur Heart J. 2015;36(33):2246-56."
            }
        ],
        "other_refer": [
            {
                "href": "",
                "text": ""
